<br>
1. Druid LvL 50.<br>
Acuity buffs have no effect on him. But with SC gear his empathy is over 210. So after the debuff his emp is about 144. That is a fairly descent drain to my mana pool. BUT! It will not affect my insta healing nor will it affect the size of my heals(I think). With the addition of power potions, bounty gems, and MCL the effect on power pool is nearly negated. I probably wouldn't even notice it. <br>
<br>
2. Enchanter Lvl 47.<br>
